<item>
            <title>[LU-17703] some pool inheritance fixes</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17703</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;a couple of problems on inheritance: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;the start index inherited from parent may conflict to the pool inherited from root what prevents new file creation;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;adjust stripe_count by the count of targets  in the pool only if the pool is not dropped on inheritance;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;a new dir does not inherit the ost list, but inherit the other LOVEA parameters, start index in particular;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
